<inglise>Amendments to State Allowances Act </inglise>
<eesti>Riiklike elatusrahade seaduses (RT 1993, 15, 256; RT I 1993, 35, 542; 74, 1055; 1994, 23, 384; 24, 397; 51, 855; 72, 1261; 1995, 14, 168; 61, 1027; 68, 1139; 95, 1631; 1996, 22, 437; 45, 849; 86, 1539; 1997, 77, 1309; 81, 1366; 1998, 17, 266) tehakse j&auml;rgmised muudatused: </eesti>
<inglise>The State Allowances Act (RT 1993, 15, 256; RT I 1993, 35, 542; 74, 1055; 1994, 23, 384; 24, 397; 51, 855; 72, 1261; 1995, 14, 168; 61, 1027; 68, 1139; 95, 1631; 1996, 22, 437; 45, 849; 86, 1539; 1997, 77, 1309; 81, 1366; 1998, 17, 266) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahvides 5, 5 (1), 6, 7 ja 41 asendatakse s&otilde;nad "pensioni&otilde;iguslik staa&zcaron;" s&otilde;nadega "pensioni&otilde;iguslik v&otilde;i pensionikindlustusstaa&zcaron;" vastavas k&auml;&auml;ndes; </eesti>
<inglise>1) in sections 5, 5 (1), 6, 7 and 41, the words "years of pensionable service" are substituted by the words "years of pensionable service or accumulation period" in the appropriate case form. </inglise>
<eesti>2) seadust t&auml;iendatakse &sect;-ga 76 (2) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>2) Section 76 (2) is added to the Act worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 76 (2). </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 76 (2). </inglise>
<eesti>Pensionikindlustusstaa&zcaron;i arvestatakse riikliku pensionikindlustuse seaduse &sect;-des 20 ja 47 s&auml;testatud korras." </eesti>
<inglise>The accumulation period shall be calculated pursuant to the procedure provided for in &sect;&sect; 20 and 47 of the State Pension Insurance Act." </inglise>
