<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;tajate distsiplinaarvastutuse seaduse (RT I 1993, 26, 441; 1995, 16, 228; 1998, 64/65, 1009; 2000, 102, 674) &sect; 17 l&otilde;ike 2 kogu tekstis asendatakse s&otilde;na "sotsiaalfondi" s&otilde;nadega "riikliku pensionikindlustuse eelarvesse". </eesti>
<inglise>In the entire text of subsection 17 (2) of the Employees Disciplinary Punishments Act (RT I 1993, 26, 441; 1995, 16, 228; 1998, 64/65, 1009; 2000, 102, 674), the words "social fund" are substituted by the words "state pension insurance budget". </inglise>
